ate, Potassium gluconate, Calcium chloride, Zinc sulfate, Magnesium sulfate, Sodium acetate, Arginine, Sodium glycerophosphate, Zinc chloride, Tromethamine, Sodium phosphate, monobasic, More', 'Tetracaine, Ketotifen, Levocetirizine, Trimethobenzamide, Terfenadine, Astemizole', 1767369485);
