ffects of these drugs and in whom toxicity symptoms may be easily overlooked.', 'Moderate', 'pharmacodynamic', NULL, 'https://ddinter2.scbdd.com/server/interact/75024/', '', 'Ketotifen, Mepyramine, Fexofenadine, Loratadine, Desloratadine, Azelastine, Terfenadine, Astemizole', 'Lidocaine, Tetracaine, Ketotifen, Fexofenadine, Thiethylperazine, Trimethobenzamide, Loratadine, Desloratadine, Azelastine, Terfenadine, Astemizole', 1767369485);
